START: LXI H, 2000H ; Load memory address 2000H into HL pair
MOV A, M ; Get value from memory
CPI 40H ; Compare with 40H
JC BELOW ; Jump to BELOW if value is less than 40H
JZ EQUAL ; Jump to EQUAL if value is equal to 40H
; If value is greater than 40H:
MVI A, 'G' ; Load 'G' (Greater) into accumulator
JMP OUTPUT ; Jump to output
BELOW: MVI A, 'L' ; Load 'L' (Lesser) into accumulator
JMP OUTPUT ; Jump to output
EQUAL: MVI A, 'E' ; Load 'E' (Equal) into accumulator
OUTPUT: STA 2050H ; Store result in memory location 2050H
HLT ; Halt the program
